# Testing Rules

- Use Vitest + fast-check property tests as the default testing style.
- Each property should run at least `numRuns: 100`.
- Name test files as `<feature>.test.ts`; for components use `<ComponentName>.test.ts`.
- Keep tests in the proper layer folder under `src/__tests__/`.
- In tests, prefer relative imports (`../../services/...`) instead of path aliases.

## Mocking Order

- Put `vi.mock(...)` calls before importing the module under test.
- For async properties, clear mocks inside each property run when needed.
- For Astro virtual modules, use stubs from `src/__tests__/__mocks__/`.

## Scope Reminder

- `src/__tests__/components/` is only for component rendering tests.
- Do not place utils/services/repositories property tests inside `components/`.
